summary: Adds fast travel locations to all buyable houses in Skyrim
descriptionHtml:
[font=\"Arial Black\"][size=4]Description:[/font][/size]

!This is the first mod I have ever made so don\'t hesitate to tell me if there are any problems.!
Or if you\'ve got some opinions or thoughts on things I could change.

This mod adds fast travel markers to all the player home houses. You will load right outside of the house that you have fast traveled to. I have also added a second location to Sky Haven Temple where you will load in the training ground.
 
[font=\"Arial Black\"][size=4]You can choose from 3 different versions:[/font][/size]
[font=\"Arial Black\"]Version 1:[/font] The locations are visible and discovered. You can fast travel to them right away. 
[font=\"Arial Black\"]Version 2:[/font]  The locations are visible but not discovered.
[font=\"Arial Black\"]Version 3:[/font]  The locations are not visible and not discovered. You will have to discover them before you can fast travel to them. The same way you have to with every location in the game.

[font=\"Arial Black\"][size=4]How to install:[/font][/size]
Just extract the esp file into your Skyrim\\Data folder

[font=\"Arial Black\"][size=4]How to uninstall:[/font][/size]
Just remove the file

[font=\"Arial Black\"][size=4]Permissions:[/font][/size]
Please ask me before uploading this somewhere else.

Endorse if you like this mod =)

------ Updates
1.1
I fixed a little detail with the Sky Haven Temple marker and the Proudspire Manor marker where  it sounded like the player was dropped down.
